 from any source<br />\nYou do not need to provide any other documents.<br />\n<br />\nWhen you register, you will get a registration certificate. This certificate confirms your right to live in your new country."},{"pid":"0a32e1981adfd56424818080d2bce2484067f376","tid":827720,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:52:19.000Z","msg":"即係你可以去個細埠仔, 少香港人去嘅，申請pr card 就得！"},{"pid":"e27e7ee19cdd94921b7873b5f45796560d862549","tid":827720,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:53:17.000Z","msg":"歐盟好大，總有容身地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8febf88cb0f3a7be73a4539ea90a7f3fec3f9b4c","tid":827720,"uid":156071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:02:28.000Z","msg":"冇用，你一去 register人地就會問<br />\n一 check到個 code係 GBN你就走得啦"},{"pid":"05c977250caee21d1b5ddbd22ad2f4633f3fd623","tid":827720,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8febf88cb0f3a7be73a4539ea90a7f3fec3f9b4c","tid":827720,"uid":156071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:02:28.000Z","msg":"冇用，你一去 register人地就會問<br />\n一 check到個 code係 GBN你就走得啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:07:57.000Z","msg":"無人叫你去D大國,傻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7244cce03e0ca370d9d0b59cd9568dcfde8292","tid":827720,"uid":156071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05c977250caee21d1b5ddbd22ad2f4633f3fd623","tid":827720,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8febf88cb0f3a7be73a4539ea90a7f3fec3f9b4c","tid":827720,"uid":156071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:02:28.000Z","msg":"冇用，你一去 register人地就會問<br />\n一 check到個 code係 GBN你就走得啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:07:57.000Z","msg":"無人叫你去D大國,傻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci